    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to hit the pavement with you! It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it still looks and drives great. I'd love to see it go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
