    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer who appreciates a well-maintained, reliable machine. The exterior maintains a brilliant finish with only very minor, age-appropriate imperfections that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean; the seats are firm and free of significant wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every button and switch operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, reflecting a history of diligent, on-time servicing. It has been primarily garage-kept, which is evident in the preservation of the trim and rubber seals. Included with the sale is a detailed log of maintenance records, ensuring peace of mind for the next owner. This car drives with the tight, composed feel of a much younger vehicle and is ready for immediate daily use or long-distance travel.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
